The evidence with the title 'Inequality gap widens as 42 people hold same wealth as 3.7bn ... ' says Jan 22, 2018  ... Oxfam calls for action on gap as wealthiest people gather at World Economic  ... A new report showing that 42 people hold as much wealth as the 3.7 billion who make up the poorest half of the world's population.  ... At a time when the bottom 50% of the world's population had seen no increase in wealth. 
